column5: Found this fun website for making your own cartoon movies.  http://www.xtranormal.com  It's a fun way to kill an hour. You can email the finished movie to friends or post it on youtube like I did with these two.    This is a John Lennon tribute, with my dance moves perfectly replicated at the end.
That killed some time while I can't sleep  http://ca.youtube.com/watch?v=m1VDkuC5jVM
Good one Dan. I'm in the same boat, worked midnights this week and now I can't sleep.
Good cartoons guys. I finally had a chance to try this out...Here it is. http://www.xtranormal.com/watch?e=2008111517355960
